    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.04)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.39)))
    v2 = (v1 / wp.cos(tmp))
    tmp = v0
    v1 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.29 * tmp + 0.50)) - wp.abs(v1))
    v0 = 0.41
    data[tid] = v0
